while the Union for French Democracy -LRB- UDF -RRB- party , led by François Bayrou , formally remains in the ruling coalition along with the UMP , it has decided that , because the new government would probably do more of the same policies , it would not participate in it .
the only member of the government from UDF is Gilles de Robien , as in the preceding government .
