his role in the contentious dispute will be to keep the peace in the town of Caledonia .
officials in Ontario and the federal governments are currently negotiating with Six Nations representatives .
both the Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam -LRB- DMK -RRB- and the All India Anna Dravida Munnetra Kazhagam -LRB- AIADMK -RRB- parties have announce `` freebies ' ' as part of their election manifestos in the lead-up to the vote in the south Indian state of Tamil Nadu .
freebies have been a success from the 2006 Tamil Nadu elections when DMK lured voters by announcing free color televisions to households .
that triumph led the major opposition AIADMK to announce similar freebies in their manifesto published Thursday .
