the comments were addenda and an accompanying note , supplemental to the original report , which was issued last autumn , and seen as the final report of the Iraq Survey Group -LRB- ISG -RRB- .
they were added by Charles Duelfer , head of the ISG , and Special Adviser to the Director of Central Intelligence in Baghdad .
