Chemist with the National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration ' s Ocean Service office of response and restoration , Jim Farr said the sulfur spill from the two freighters would n 't create a `` hazardous situation ' ' , a statement backed up by Alexei Zhukovin , expert with the Emergency Situations Ministry ' s branch in Southern Russia .
